Universal link from Splunk
https://docs.splunk.com/Documentation/Forwarder/9.2.0/Forwarder/InstallaWindowsuniversalforwarderfromaninstaller

Step by Step Process for Installer
1. Download the file from the universal link

2. Install the msi executable file

3. While Creating the installation create a admin username and password for setting up

4. Configure the Deployment Server and Receiving Indexer using with host name or IP address and management port provided by Organization.
